==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Pendency
<hw>Pend"en*cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
quality or state of being pendent or suspended.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The quality or state of being undecided, or in
continuance; suspense; <as>as, the <ex>pendency</ex> of a
suit</as>.</def> <rj><au>Ayliffe.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Pendent</ent>⟦br⟧
